# PUBLICATION PATHWAY

## Paper 1: Validation Study
**Target:** Journal of College Student Development or Journal of American College Health
**Title:** "CheckIn: Validation of an Ultra-Brief Screening Tool for Residential Student Wellbeing"
**Timeline:** Pilot Fall 2026, submit Spring 2027

## Paper 2: Topology-Wellbeing
**Target:** NASPA Journal About Women in Higher Education or Journal of College Student Retention
**Title:** "Social Network Topology and Psychological Wellbeing in Residential College Students: A Homological Analysis"
**Timeline:** Data collection 2026-27, submit Fall 2027

## Paper 3: Intervention
**Target:** Journal of Student Affairs Research and Practice
**Title:** "Topology-Informed Interventions in Residence Life: A Randomized Controlled Trial"
**Timeline:** Intervention 2027-28, submit 2028

